  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t今天刷到一条的新闻，说是日本的首相，岸田文雄吃完福岛海鲜不到一个小时，身体不适被紧急送医：   新闻来源<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvNWJiNGRjYWQzZDJkNTRhZTI1Y2NjLmpwZz93aWR0aD05MDAmaGVpZ2h0PTE3Nw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/5bb4dcad3d2d54ae25ccc.jpg?width=900&amp;height=177\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/5bb4dcad3d2d54ae25ccc.jpg?width=900&amp;height=177\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/5bb4dcad3d2d54ae25ccc.jpg?width=900&amp;height=177\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\r\n新闻内容如正标题所诉，然后配上一个图片，图片里一个蓝布盖着脸的人正在被担架抬走：<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvMThkNWQ5NjYzNDRmZTVhN2I2ODIwLmpwZz93aWR0aD04NzgmaGVpZ2h0PTc1OA\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/18d5d966344fe5a7b6820.jpg?width=878&amp;height=758\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/18d5d966344fe5a7b6820.jpg?width=878&amp;height=758\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/18d5d966344fe5a7b6820.jpg?width=878&amp;height=758\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\r\n在Google上搜索这张图片，结果发现这张图是去年安培遇刺时拍的照片：<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvYTlmMDA3ZmMwOWE0ZGM0ZTI0YjIyLmpwZz93aWR0aD0xODY2JmhlaWdodD05MTY\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/a9f007fc09a4dc4e24b22.jpg?width=1866&amp;height=916\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/a9f007fc09a4dc4e24b22.jpg?width=1866&amp;height=916\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/a9f007fc09a4dc4e24b22.jpg?width=1866&amp;height=916\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\r\n在百度上搜索新闻标题，发现很多相似新闻，不同点在于标注了\"日媒爆料\"，当然文章内并没有附上日媒爆料的来源：<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvMDEwNDliNzU0N2FkMjAyNWNmNzMwLmpwZz93aWR0aD0xMDgyJmhlaWdodD05MTg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/01049b7547ad2025cf730.jpg?width=1082&amp;height=918\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/01049b7547ad2025cf730.jpg?width=1082&amp;height=918\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/01049b7547ad2025cf730.jpg?width=1082&amp;height=918\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\r\n在BBC上搜索关键词Japan，按时间排序的前三条新闻分别是报道中国民众对日本的愤怒，以及日本首相试吃福岛水域的生鱼。其中并没有首相岸田文雄身体不适的有关新闻：<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvZmZjZDA0YTY5MzAxMGQ5NDRlNmNkLmpwZz93aWR0aD04ODMmaGVpZ2h0PTgxNA\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/ffcd04a693010d944e6cd.jpg?width=883&amp;height=814\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/ffcd04a693010d944e6cd.jpg?width=883&amp;height=814\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/ffcd04a693010d944e6cd.jpg?width=883&amp;height=814\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\r\n在Google上用英文搜索有关首相身体不适的新闻，限定时间为一周内，没有相关搜索结果：<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvYjA2YTdjY2MwMGU4NjY3Nzk2NDQ1LmpwZz93aWR0aD0xNTc5JmhlaWdodD04NjI\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/b06a7ccc00e8667796445.jpg?width=1579&amp;height=862\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/b06a7ccc00e8667796445.jpg?width=1579&amp;height=862\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/b06a7ccc00e8667796445.jpg?width=1579&amp;height=862\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\r\n换成日文在Google上搜索，同样没有相关结果：<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvMWEzNGM5MmMxZDE5ZTIxNjhkNGUwLmpwZz93aWR0aD0xNTUyJmhlaWdodD04OTg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/1a34c92c1d19e2168d4e0.jpg?width=1552&amp;height=898\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/1a34c92c1d19e2168d4e0.jpg?width=1552&amp;height=898\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/1a34c92c1d19e2168d4e0.jpg?width=1552&amp;height=898\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\r\n到这里结论就已经很明显了，首相身体不适住院这种大事发生在日本这个有新闻自由的国家，不可能会毫无风声。外网没有一点首相病倒相关信息，只能证明这个墙内新闻纯属是在造谣。\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>",
